KUBIKWA ukuthi ithathwe yisifo sikashukela indoda (77) yaseMiroram, e-India, ebisidume umhlaba wonke ngokuba nenqwaba yamakhosikazi nezingane. UMnuz Ziona Chana, obezigqaja ngesithembu sakhe, kuthiwa ubenamakhosikazi awu-38 nezingane eziwu-89. Kuthiwa lo wesilisa kuke kwaba khona unyaka lapho aganwa khona amakhosikazi awu-10 kanti waqalwa ukuganwa eneminyaka engu-17. UNgqongqoshe waseMizoram, uMnuz Zoramthanga, umemezele ukushona kukaChana ngesonto enkundleni yokuxhumana uTwitter. Uthe: “Siphuke izinhliziyo njengoba sivalelisa kuMnuz Chan okukholakala ukuthi unomndeni omkhulu umhlaba wonke,” kubeka uZoramthanga. Kuthiwa le ndawo yaseMizoram iphenduke indawo egcwala izivakashi zamanye amazwe bezobona lo mndeni. Umndeni kaChan kuthiwa uhlala esitezi esinamagumbi awu-100 kanti amakhosikazi akhe alala egunjini elikhulu eliseceleni kwelakhe. Kuthiwa uChan ubenesonto lakhe, iChana Pawl, elinamalungu awu-2 000 nokuyilona elivumela isithembu kule ndawo. Leli sonto, elingaphansi kwenkolo yobuKrestu, laqalwa nguyise ngo-1942. Usopolitiki wenhlangano, iCongress party, uMnuz Lal Thanhawla, uthe balahlekelwe kakhulu. “Kuningi esingakufunda emndenini wakhe,” kusho uThanhawla. UChan ushiye abazukulu abawu-33. 